UID:2026-03-03T10:00:00+01:00--4186277645941006554@leekduck-calendar
DESCRIPTION:Welcome to Pokémon GO: Memories in Motion!\n\nIn Pokémon GO\
 , Seasons are periods of time that feature new events\, Pokémon debuts\, 
 and surprises that all follow a certain theme. As the Seasons change\, you
  may find different Pokémon appearing in your area and hatching from Eggs
 . Make sure to explore during each in-game Season to collect and train as 
 many different Pokémon as you can! You’ll also enjoy special bonuses as
  you do.\n\nMore info: https://leekduck.com/events/season-22-memories-in-m
 otion/\n\nData from LeekDuck.com
LOCATION:Pokemon GO
URL:https://leekduck.com/events/season-22-memories-in-motion/
